Raymour & Flanigan Delivery Areas






		
       We currently offer white-glove, in-home furniture and mattress delivery service within 3 days or less to most zip codes in 
	   Connecticut, 
           Delaware, 
	   New York, 
           New Jersey, 
           Rhode Island,
           Massachusetts and 
           Pennsylvania. 
We can also deliver in 2-4 weeks to parts of 
Washington D.C., Maine, Maryland, New Hampshire and Vermont. Deliveries to Virginia, North Carolina, South Carolina, Georgia 
and Florida are generally made within 3-5 weeks. Plus, we offer nationwide free shipping on most home decor and area rugs.
        
	




Do we deliver to your area?



















94043 - Mountain View, CA

qualifies for FREE Home Décor & Area Rug Shipping* OR Free In-Store Furniture or Mattress Pick-up





	DELIVERY POLICIES & TIMING




	        Furniture & Mattress Delivery
        
        Sorry, we are unable to deliver furniture and mattresses to this zip code. You can always choose In-Store Pickup.
    


	        Free FedEx/UPS Shipping
        
        Most home décor items and area rugs qualify for free shipping. 
    

        Home décor & online-only labeled product should arrive in 5-10 days. Once your order has been shipped, we will email the tracking number to you.
    

        Rugs are shipped factory-direct for free. Most deliveries arrive within 3 weeks, but some could take up to 6 weeks. Once your order has been shipped, we will send you the tracking number.
    




                            DELIVERY FEES
                        

Delivery Fees to "94043"
Free Delivery of Home Décor & Area Rugs


In-Store Pickup Includes**

Unlimited furniture items
Furniture is available for pickup within a few days from most Raymour and Flanigan showrooms



    AVAILABLE OPTIONS IN THIS AREA



Flexible Financing





	RETURN POLICIES



        We are proud to offer quality products with great value to our customers. Merchandise received in good condition is not returnable or cancellable. No refunds are available.
    

        If you have chosen to pick up your order from one of our showrooms, we encourage you to inspect your items before you take possession.
    

        In the rare occurrence that an item arrives damaged on delivery or is otherwise damaged before your possession, please notify the delivery team or a customer care representative of the damage. For home décor, arrangements will be made to exchange the item. 
    


            Area Rugs
        
        Rug & online-only labeled product exchanges and returns are handled by contacting our customer care department at 1.866.383.4484 (option 2). Please note: all returns for accommodations require a restocking fee of 10%.
    










	
